metadata.name: SALVATION
metadata.description:
Title: SALVATION

The first artwork of the 'Journey Through Worlds' collection.

The winning collector will receive the original PNG file (numbered as #1 and signed) in 6000 x 4926 pixel.

All bidders will receive a numbered and signed PNG file of artwork in 2000 x 1642 pixel.

Artwork by Philip Sue and created on Adobe Photoshop.
